data.description: Beautiful two story home in Alderwood neighborhood. A large great room concept downstairs gives plenty of room gatherings. A powder room at the entry is perfect for guests. A custom entertainment unit provides plenty of storage and is equipped with a drink refrigerator and a kegerator. The perfectly situated TV will stay with the home! Upstairs you will be greeted by a cozy landing, a full size bath, 2 secondary bedrooms, a bonus room, and the large master bedroom. The bonus room is currently a music room, but has endless possibilities, an office, a playroom, a second living room, or event convert it to a 4th bedroom.    The yards are low maintenance with drought tolerate plants and artificial turf. The side yard is being used for a beautiful vegetable and fruit garden. Their is plenty of room to add a beautiful pool. This home has a tankless water heater,  fire sprinkler system, water softener, reverse osmosis in the kitchen, and a permitted Tesla charging station. The kitchen refrigerator and washer and dryer convey with the sell.    Pest inspection cleared and has an assumable VA Loan at 3%.
